### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:4080
@adminEmail = admin@cody.inc
@adminPassword = password

### Get Auth Token
# @name login
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/auth/email/login
accept: application/json
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "{{adminEmail}}",
  "password": "{{adminPassword}}"
}

###
### ===========================================
### GET REVIEW ENDPOINTS
### ===========================================

### Get All Reviews
# @name getAllReviews
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/reviews?skip=0&take=20
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.token}}

### Get Reviews by Service
# @name getServiceReviews
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/reviews/services/1/reviews
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.token}}

### Get Reviews by Seller
# @name getSellerReviews
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/reviews/sellers/1/reviews
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.token}}

### Get Review by ID
# @name getReviewById
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/reviews/1
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.token}}

### Get Reviews with Filters
# @name getReviewsWithFilters
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/reviews?service_id=1&reviewable_type=service&rating=5&skip=0&take=20
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.token}}

###
### ===========================================
### CREATE REVIEW ENDPOINTS
### ===========================================

### Create Product Review
# @name createProductReview
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/reviews
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.token}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW

------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="seller_id"

1
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="product_id"

1
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="reviewable_type"

product
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="rating"

5
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="comment"

Excellent product! Highly recommended.
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="is_anonymous"

false
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="is_verified_purchase"

true
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW--

### Create Service Review (via booking)
# @name createBookingReview
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/reviews/bookings/1/review
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.token}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW

------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="rating"

5
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="comment"

Excellent service! The provider was punctual and professional.
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="is_anonymous"

false
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="aspect_ratings[punctuality]"

5
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="aspect_ratings[quality]"

5
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="aspect_ratings[communication]"

4
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="aspect_ratings[professionalism]"

5
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW--

### Create Service Review (direct)
# @name createServiceReview
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/reviews
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.token}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW

------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="seller_id"

1
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="service_id"

1
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="reviewable_type"

service
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="source_type"

booking
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="source_id"

1
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="rating"

5
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="comment"

Great service experience!
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="aspect_ratings[punctuality]"

5
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="aspect_ratings[quality]"

5
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW--

###
### ===========================================
### UPDATE REVIEW ENDPOINTS
### ===========================================

### Update Review
# @name updateReview
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/reviews/1
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "rating": 4,
  "comment": "Updated review comment",
  "aspect_ratings": {
    "punctuality": 5,
    "quality": 4,
    "communication": 4,
    "professionalism": 5
  }
}

### Reply to Review (Seller)
# @name replyToReview
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/reviews/1/respond
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "reply_text": "Thank you for your feedback! We're glad you enjoyed our service."
}

###
### ===========================================
### DELETE REVIEW ENDPOINTS
### ===========================================

### Delete Review
# @name deleteReview
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/reviews/1
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.token}}

###
### ===========================================
### ADMIN ENDPOINTS
### ===========================================

### Update Review Status (Admin)
# @name updateReviewStatus
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/reviews/1/status
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "Removed"
}



